 	<description>
	    <p>multiCurrency allows monitoring of both direct and reverse quotes cross-rates of major world currencies.
	        If you change the value of rate indicates the direction of change - up, down, unchanged.
	    </p>
	    <p>Features:</p>
	    <ul>
            <li>It has a simple and clear interface.</li>
            <li>A customizable online multilingual translation of the application interface.</li>
	    </ul>
 	</description>

